                  "answerKey": "answer_1",
                  "content": "The communist style demanded obedience, while the capitalist style encourages independent thinking."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "The communist style focused on critical thinking skills, while the capitalist style focused on trade skills."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
                  "content": "The communist style allowed education to lapse, while the capitalist style has fully funded it."
                },
